HEADWORD: Cachiri
<hw>Ca*chi"ri</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A fermented
liquor made in Cayenne from the grated root of the manioc, and
resembling perry.</def> <rj><au>Dunglison.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
